text.tspan: Percent point differences of regional age structures

flowRoot.flowPara: Regions with an age structure close to the European average are colored in shades of grey.
The further a region's age structure deviates from the average, the brighter and vivid the corresponding color.
Hue marks the direction of deviation from the average. More young vs. more working age vs. more elderly.
